us.ihmc.euclid.referenceFrame.tools

Interface EuclidFrameAPITestTools.FrameTypeBuilder<T extends ReferenceFrameHolder>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type this builder can instantiate.
    Enclosing class:
    EuclidFrameAPITestTools

    public static interface EuclidFrameAPITestTools.FrameTypeBuilder<T extends ReferenceFrameHolder>
    Implement this interface to create builders for frame types such as FrameQuaternion.

    The frame objects created using this builder should be initialized using the given reference frame and frameless object.

        T newInstance(ReferenceFrame referenceFrame,
              java.lang.Object framelessObject)
        Creates a new instance of the frame type.

        The frame objects created using this builder should be initialized using the given reference frame and frameless object.

        Parameters:
        referenceFrame - the reference frame in which the returned frame object should be expressed in.
        framelessObject - the frameless object to use for initializing the values of the new frame object.
        Returns:
        the new frame object.
